defaultWe measure impact through 
defaultlevels of informed engagement with gove
defaultrnance debate and service delivery; youth motivation and engagement in political processes; and local media capacity to support more constructive and objective governance debate 
defaultand engagement
default in OPT
default. 
defaultAfter the first year, our nationally representative data show 
defaultthat both programmes are already achieving many of these targets
default. (86% of those watching believe that the shows are playing a role in holding government to account and 83%
default report improved understanding of governance or conflict-relevant issues as a result of watching the shows)
