default17. 
defaultBecause of the way the OPT is laid out geographically – spanning two different regions and without free movement between them – it’s not possible to have a fully representative studio audience that cuts across all segments of society. Under such circumstan
defaultces, social media is a particularly powerful tool for enabling 
defaultpeople from different areas to voice their opinions and become part of the process 
defaultof
default holding their leaders to account
default.
default18.  
defaultPalestinians are 
defaulto
defaultverwhelmingly young
